Understand the uncertainty in CMIP6 dataset

There exists uncertainty in model simulations, which is the reason that we need multipul models and multipul ensembles. Here in this notebook, we show the different temperature trend shown among the 6 members of the ssp126 experiment of CNRM-CM6-1 model in CMIP6 archive.

[17]:

import xarray as xr

[18]:

!clef cmip6 --activity ScenarioMIP \
           --table  Amon          \
           --grid   gr            \
           --variable   tas        \
           --experiment  ssp126    \
           --model      CNRM-CM6-1
